Cloud types:
two types - Service Model and Deployment Model
coming to service model -> IAAS,PAAS,SAAS
IAAS->we have to maintain 50% and coming to cloud will maitain 50%
PAAS->we have to maintain 20% and coming to cloud will maitain 80%
SAAS->we have to maintain 0% and coming to cloud will maitain 100%
Now comming to Deployment model
PUBLIC - nothing like AWS and AZURE service 
PRIVATE - physical servers.
HYBRID - half part public and half part(secure part) private
CUMMUNITY -> single DATACENTER they will maintain both companies.
